{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1777082987994,"sessionID":"ses_23d9a4e4dffeFPgRJE0V5TcCHZ","part":{"type":"tool","tool":"read","callID":"call_kKqi4sVrITUTVG0L71oUmNln","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"D:\\agent_workspace\\capability-library\\mycli\\README.md","limit":220,"offset":1},"output":"<path>D:\\agent_workspace\\capability-library\\mycli\\README.md</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>\n1: # mycli\n2: \n3: `mycli` 是 `D:\\agent_workspace\\capability-library` 的统一命令入口。\n4: \n5: 它把能力包、脚本、现有 CLI 工具组织成一套可发现、可说明、可执行的命令体系。\n6: \n7: ## Usage\n8: \n9: ```powershell\n10: mycli --help\n11: mycli list\n12: mycli package list\n13: mycli package register <package/path> --summary <text> --source <text>\n14: mycli package register-full <package/path> --summary <text> --source <text> --commands <json> --help <markdown>\n15: mycli <package...> --help\n16: mycli <package...> list\n17: mycli <package...> command list\n18: mycli <package...> command register <name> --summary <text> --entry <absolute-path> --args <json> [--prefix-args <json>]\n19: mycli <package...> command register-many --commands <json>\n20: mycli <package...> command update <name> [--summary <text>] [--entry <absolute-path>] [--args <json>] [--prefix-args <json>]\n21: mycli <package...> help update --content <markdown>\n22: mycli <package...> <command> [args...]\n23: ```\n24: \n25: ## Core Ideas\n26: \n27: - `package`\n28:   一个能力包\n29: - `subpackage`\n30:   包下面的子包，目录即层级\n31: - `command`\n32:   包里的具体执行动作\n33: - `cli.package.json`\n34:   包注册中心\n35: - `README.md`\n36:   包级帮助内容来源\n37: \n38: ## Common Flows\n39: \n40: 查看所有顶层包：\n41: \n42: ```powershell\n43: mycli list\n44: ```\n45: \n46: 查看某个包的完整说明：\n47: \n48: ```powershell\n49: mycli opencode --help\n50: ```\n51: \n52: 查看某个包里有哪些子包和命令：\n53: \n54: ```powershell\n55: mycli opencode list\n56: ```\n57: \n58: 执行某个命令：\n59: \n60: ```powershell\n61: mycli opencode run \"hello\"\n62: ```\n63: \n64: 查看并使用 workflow 能力：\n65: \n66: ```powershell\n67: mycli agent-workflow --help\n68: mycli agent-workflow list\n69: mycli agent-workflow validate D:\\agent_workspace\\capability-library\\agent-system-rules\\agent-workflow\\examples\\script_echo_flow\n70: ```\n71: \n72: ## opencode Example\n73: \n74: `opencode` 目前同时支持两种方式：\n75: \n76: 直接映射命令：\n77: \n78: ```powershell\n79: mycli opencode run \"hello\"\n80: mycli opencode models --help\n81: mycli opencode agent --help\n82: ```\n83: \n84: 原生透传：\n85: \n86: ```powershell\n87: mycli opencode native --help\n88: mycli opencode native run hello\n89: mycli opencode native models --help\n90: ```\n91: \n92: ## agent-workflow Example\n93: \n94: `agent-workflow` 适合把多步骤任务建模成可运行、可等待、可审核的 workflow。\n95: \n96: ```powershell\n97: mycli agent-workflow init D:\\agent_workspace\\projects\\my-flow --workflow-id my_flow --name \"My Flow\"\n98: mycli agent-workflow scaffold D:\\agent_workspace\\projects\\my-flow\n99: mycli agent-workflow validate D:\\agent_workspace\\projects\\my-flow\n100: mycli agent-workflow graph D:\\agent_workspace\\projects\\my-flow\n101: mycli agent-workflow start-run D:\\agent_workspace\\capability-library\\agent-system-rules\\agent-workflow\\examples\\script_echo_flow\n102: ```\n103: \n104: 单次 agent 调用优先用 `mycli agent-cli run`。\n105: 多步骤、可等待、可审核、带运行状态的流程优先用 `mycli agent-workflow ...`。\n106: \n107: ## Docs\n108: \n109: 用户手册：\n110: \n111: - `D:\\agent_workspace\\capability-library\\mycli\\common\\user-manual.md`\n112: \n113: 维护与技术手册：\n114: \n115: - `D:\\agent_workspace\\capability-library\\mycli\\common\\technical-manual.md`\n\n(End of file - total 115 lines)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"# mycli\n\n`mycli` 是 `D:\\agent_workspace\\capability-library` 的统一命令入口。\n\n它把能力包、脚本、现有 CLI 工具组织成一套可发现、可说明、可执行的命令体系。\n\n## Usage\n\n```powershell\nmycli --help\nmycli list\nmycli package list\nmycli package register <package/path> --summary <text> --source <text>\nmycli package register-full <package/path> --summary <text> --source <text> --commands <json> --help <markdown>\nmycli <package...> --help\nmycli <package...> list\nmycli <package...> command list\nmycli <package...> command register <name> --summary <text> --entry <absolute-path> --args <json> [--prefix-args <json>]\nmycli <package...> command register-many --commands <json>\nmycli <package...> command update <name> [--summary <text>] [--entry <absolute-path>] [--args <json>] [--prefix-args <json>]","truncated":false,"loaded":[]},"title":"agent_workspace\\capability-library\\mycli\\README.md","time":{"start":1777082987805,"end":1777082987993}},"id":"prt_dc2667519001P1LjyQHQNwLmCK","sessionID":"ses_23d9a4e4dffeFPgRJE0V5TcCHZ","messageID":"msg_dc2664276001HOosd8ENsDduzY"}}
{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1777082988002,"sessionID":"ses_23d9a4e4dffeFPgRJE0V5TcCHZ","part":{"type":"tool","tool":"read","callID":"call_N7E6mPEKVB3u41cIcUPK5x5K","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"D:\\agent_workspace\\capability-library\\mycli\\common\\technical-manual.md","limit":260,"offset":1},"output":"<path>D:\\agent_workspace\\capability-library\\mycli\\common\\technical-manual.md</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>\n1: # mycli 维护与技术手册\n2: \n3: ## 1. 文档目的\n4: \n5: 这份文档面向后续维护 `mycli` 的技术人员。\n6: \n7: 目标是帮助后续继续做这些事情：\n8: \n9: - 新增能力包\n10: - 调整命令注册结构\n11: - 修改帮助展示逻辑\n12: - 接入已有外部 CLI\n13: - 排查运行时问题\n14: \n15: ---\n16: \n17: ## 2. 当前目录结构\n18: \n19: 当前根目录：\n20: \n21: ```text\n22: D:\\agent_workspace\\capability-library\\mycli\n23: ```\n24: \n25: 关键文件：\n26: \n27: - `mycli.ps1`\n28:   PowerShell 主入口包装器\n29: - `mycli.cmd`\n30:   Windows 命令行包装器\n31: - `common\\cli.ps1`\n32:   核心运行时实现\n33: - `common\\requirements.md`\n34:   需求与设计收敛文档\n35: - `common\\user-manual.md`\n36:   面向用户的使用手册\n37: - `common\\technical-manual.md`\n38:   本文档\n39: \n40: 包目录示例：\n41: \n42: ```text\n43: mycli\\\n44:   opencode\\\n45:     cli.package.json\n46:     README.md\n47: ```\n48: \n49: ---\n50: \n51: ## 3. 核心设计模型\n52: \n53: `mycli` 的核心对象有 4 类：\n54: \n55: - `package`\n56:   能力包\n57: - `subpackage`\n58:   子包，目录即层级\n59: - `command`\n60:   包内可执行命令\n61: - `help`\n62:   包级文档，来自 `README.md`\n63: \n64: 核心设计原则：\n65: \n66: - 包树使用目录结构表示\n67: - 每个包目录使用 `cli.package.json` 作为注册中心\n68: - 每个包目录使用 `README.md` 作为 `--help` 数据源\n69: - `entry` 统一使用绝对路径\n70: - 命令参数采用结构化 `args`\n71: - 外部 CLI 可以通过“直接转发”或“前缀转发”接入\n72: \n73: ---\n74: \n75: ## 4. 运行时职责分层\n76: \n77: ### `mycli.ps1`\n78: \n79: 负责把用户输入传给核心脚本：\n80: \n81: - 作为 PowerShell 入口\n82: - 调用 `common\\cli.ps1`\n83: \n84: ### `mycli.cmd`\n85: \n86: 负责兼容 `cmd` 场景：\n87: \n88: - 作为批处理入口\n89: - 再转到 PowerShell 入口\n90: \n91: ### `common\\cli.ps1`\n92: \n93: 这是整个系统的核心。\n94: \n95: 主要职责：\n96: \n97: - 参数解析\n98: - 路径与包定位\n99: - 包配置读取与写入\n100: - 命令注册与更新\n101: - README 帮助读取与写入\n102: - 已注册命令的实际执行\n103: \n104: ---\n105: \n106: ## 5. 包结构约定\n107: \n108: 任意包目录都应当至少包含：\n109: \n110: - `cli.package.json`\n111: - `README.md`\n112: \n113: 示例：\n114: \n115: ```text\n116: D:\\agent_workspace\\capability-library\\mycli\\opencode\\\n117:   cli.package.json\n118:   README.md\n119: ```\n120: \n121: 嵌套包示例：\n122: \n123: ```text\n124: D:\\agent_workspace\\capability-library\\mycli\\dev\\\n125:   cli.package.json\n126:   README.md\n127:   opencli\\\n128:     cli.package.json\n129:     README.md\n130: ```\n131: \n132: ---\n133: \n134: ## 6. `cli.package.json` 结构\n135: \n136: 当前最核心字段：\n137: \n138: ```json\n139: {\n140:   \"name\": \"opencode\",\n141:   \"summary\": \"Forwarding package for the existing opencode CLI\",\n142:   \"source\": \"D:\\\\agent_workspace\\\\projects\\\\opencode\",\n143:   \"commands\": [\n144:     {\n145:       \"name\": \"run\",\n146:       \"summary\": \"Run opencode with a message\",\n147:       \"args\": [\n148:         {\n149:           \"name\": \"message\",\n150:           \"required\": false,\n151:           \"summary\": \"Message to send to opencode\",\n152:           \"type\": \"string\"\n153:         }\n154:       ],\n155:       \"prefixArgs\": [\n156:         \"run\"\n157:       ],\n158:       \"entry\": \"C:\\\\Users\\\\38188\\\\AppData\\\\Roaming\\\\npm\\\\opencode.ps1\"\n159:     }\n160:   ]\n161: }\n162: ```\n163: \n164: 字段说明：\n165: \n166: - `name`\n167:   包名，通常等于目录名\n168: - `summary`\n169:   顶层 `list` 或子包展示时的一句话简介\n170: - `source`\n171:   来源描述，推荐绝对路径，也允许自定义文本\n172: - `commands`\n173:   命令注册数组\n174: \n175: 命令对象字段：\n176: \n177: - `name`\n178:   命令名\n179: - `summary`\n180:   命令简介\n181: - `args`\n182:   结构化参数说明\n183: - `entry`\n184:   绝对路径入口\n185: - `prefixArgs`\n186:   可选。固定插入到实际执行前面的参数数组\n187: \n188: ---\n189: \n190: ## 7. `prefixArgs` 的作用\n191: \n192: 这是当前支持“原生 CLI 包装”的关键机制。\n193: \n194: ### 直接透传\n195: \n196: 例如：\n197: \n198: ```json\n199: {\n200:   \"name\": \"native\",\n201:   \"summary\": \"Forward all remaining arguments to opencode\",\n202:   \"args\": [],\n203:   \"entry\": \"C:\\\\Users\\\\38188\\\\AppData\\\\Roaming\\\\npm\\\\opencode.ps1\"\n204: }\n205: ```\n206: \n207: 此时：\n208: \n209: ```powershell\n210: mycli opencode native run hello\n211: ```\n212: \n213: 会执行：\n214: \n215: ```powershell\n216: opencode run hello\n217: ```\n218: \n219: ### 前缀转发\n220: \n221: 例如：\n222: \n223: ```json\n224: {\n225:   \"name\": \"run\",\n226:   \"summary\": \"Run opencode with a message\",\n227:   \"args\": [],\n228:   \"prefixArgs\": [\"run\"],\n229:   \"entry\": \"C:\\\\Users\\\\38188\\\\AppData\\\\Roaming\\\\npm\\\\opencode.ps1\"\n230: }\n231: ```\n232: \n233: 此时：\n234: \n235: ```powershell\n236: mycli opencode run hello\n237: ```\n238: \n239: 会执行：\n240: \n241: ```powershell\n242: opencode run hello\n243: ```\n244: \n245: 所以：\n246: \n247: - `native` 适合原样透传\n248: - `prefixArgs` 适合把原生子命令重定义成 `mycli` 的直接命令\n249: \n250: ---\n251: \n252: ## 8. 当前命令行为\n253: \n254: ### 顶层\n255: \n256: - `mycli --help`\n257: - `mycli list`\n258: - `mycli package list`\n259: - `mycli package register`\n260: - `mycli package register-full`\n\n(Showing lines 1-260 of 525. Use offset=261 to continue.)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"# mycli 维护与技术手册\n\n## 1. 文档目的\n\n这份文档面向后续维护 `mycli` 的技术人员。\n\n目标是帮助后续继续做这些事情：\n\n- 新增能力包\n- 调整命令注册结构\n- 修改帮助展示逻辑\n- 接入已有外部 CLI\n- 排查运行时问题\n\n---\n\n## 2. 当前目录结构\n\n当前根目录：\n","truncated":true,"loaded":[]},"title":"agent_workspace\\capability-library\\mycli\\common\\technical-manual.md","time":{"start":1777082987933,"end":1777082988001}},"id":"prt_dc266751e0010d9IZAf2H9vtxO","sessionID":"ses_23d9a4e4dffeFPgRJE0V5TcCHZ","messageID":"msg_dc2664276001HOosd8ENsDduzY"}}
