{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1777083014148,"sessionID":"ses_23d9a4e4dffeFPgRJE0V5TcCHZ","part":{"type":"tool","tool":"task","callID":"call_JI59lynGV9sLTWuyQbv5jGrp","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"category":"quick","command":"analyze-mode","description":"Map workspace capabilities","load_skills":[],"prompt":"In D:\\agent_workspace, quickly inspect the workspace with focus on capability-library and mycli. Identify the most relevant existing capabilities, notable packages, and any patterns useful for future project requirement analysis. Return a concise structured summary in Chinese. Do not modify files.","run_in_background":false,"session_id":"","subagent_type":""},"output":"SUPERVISED TASK COMPLETED SUCCESSFULLY\n\nIMPORTANT: This model (MoreCode/gemini-3-flash) is marked as unstable/experimental.\nYour run_in_background=false was automatically converted to background mode for reliability monitoring.\n\nDuration: 26s\nAgent: Sisyphus-Junior (category: quick)\n\nMONITORING INSTRUCTIONS:\n- The task was monitored and completed successfully\n- If you observe this agent behaving erratically in future calls, actively monitor its progress\n- Use background_cancel(task_id=\"...\") to abort if the agent seems stuck or producing garbage output\n- Do NOT retry automatically if you see this message - the task already succeeded\n\n---\n\nRESULT:\n\n以下是关于 `D:\\agent_workspace` 核心能力库与 `mycli` 体系的结构化调研总结：\n\n### 1. 核心架构设计 (The \"mycli\" Framework)\n`mycli` 是整个工作区的统一命令入口（PowerShell 驱动），其核心逻辑在于**“目录即层级，JSON 即注册”**。\n- **入口**: `mycli.ps1` (及 `mycli.cmd`)。\n- **注册机制**: 每个能力包通过 `cli.package.json` 定义命令，通过 `README.md` 提供帮助文档。\n- **组织结构**:\n  - `package`: 顶层功能模块。\n  - `subpackage`: 嵌套的子模块目录。\n  - `command`: 具体的执行动作，通过 `entry` 指定脚本绝对路径。\n\n### 2. 重点能力包 (Notable Packages in `mycli`)\n- **`agent-cli`**: 统一的 Agent 运行层，适配多种 Provider（如 OpenCode, Codex），支持 Session 管理和模型切换。\n- **`agent-workflow`**: 任务编排引擎。支持将复杂任务建模为可运行、可验证、带状态追踪的 Workflow。\n- **`skill-library`**: 技能索引层。对接 `capability-library\\skill-library` 下的实体技能。\n- **`opencode`**: 对 OpenCode 原生 CLI 的封装与增强。\n- **`project-manager`**: 用于管理工作区内的项目生命周期。\n\n### 3. 技能库概览 (Capability Highlights in `skill-library`)\n技能库包含 35 个以上独立包，涵盖了从底层能力到垂直场景的广泛覆盖：\n- **基础设施/Agent 增强**:\n  - `elite-longterm-memory`: 长期记忆系统。\n  - `self-improving-agent`: 自我进化 Agent 框架。\n  - `agent-browser`: 浏览器自动化能力。\n- **多媒体与 AI 处理**:\n  - `whisper-local-stt` & `gptsovits-voice-suite`: 语音识别与合成。\n  - `remotion-video-toolkit` & `after-effects-mcp`: 视频自动化编辑。\n  - `indextts`: Python 驱动的 TTS 套件。\n- **开发者工具**:\n  - `openclaw-github-assistant`: GitHub 协作集成。\n  - `skill-creator`: 用于快速生成新技能的脚手架。\n  - `harness-cli`: 自动化测试与评估工具。\n\n### 4. 关键模式与实践建议\n- **命令调用优先顺序**: \n  - 单次 Agent 调用使用 `mycli agent-cli run`。\n  - 多步骤、需持久化状态的任务使用 `mycli agent-workflow`。\n- **扩展模式**: 若要增加新能力，应在 `skill-library` 创建包并包含 `SKILL.md`，随后通过 `mycli skill-library register` 完成索引。\n- **路径依赖**: `mycli` 及其子命令强依赖于**绝对路径**，在分析需求时需确保环境路径的一致性。\n\n该结构体现了高度的**模块化**与**可插拔性**，`mycli` 作为粘合层实现了异构工具（Node.js, Python, PowerShell）的统一调用界面。\n\n<task_metadata>\nsession_id: ses_23d998b11ffeNp1CGO1i76XnVR\n</task_metadata>\n\nto continue: task(session_id=\"ses_23d998b11ffeNp1CGO1i76XnVR\", load_skills=[], run_in_background=false, prompt=\"...\")","metadata":{"truncated":false,"prompt":"In D:\\agent_workspace, quickly inspect the workspace with focus on capability-library and mycli. Identify the most relevant existing capabilities, notable packages, and any patterns useful for future project requirement analysis. Return a concise structured summary in Chinese. Do not modify files.","agent":"Sisyphus-Junior","category":"quick","load_skills":[],"description":"Map workspace capabilities","run_in_background":false,"sessionId":"ses_23d998b11ffeNp1CGO1i76XnVR","command":"analyze-mode","model":{"providerID":"MoreCode","modelID":"gemini-3-flash"}},"title":"Map workspace capabilities","time":{"start":1777082987733,"end":1777083014147}},"id":"prt_dc26674d1001wmhqxn5mGslYHg","sessionID":"ses_23d9a4e4dffeFPgRJE0V5TcCHZ","messageID":"msg_dc2664276001HOosd8ENsDduzY"}}
{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1777083022439,"sessionID":"ses_23d9a4e4dffeFPgRJE0V5TcCHZ","part":{"type":"tool","tool":"task","callID":"call_UP7FOsXgvC5Gar7Nz6wkpbUj","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"category":"quick","command":"analyze-mode","description":"Survey skill library","load_skills":[],"prompt":"In D:\\agent_workspace, quickly inspect capability-library/skill-library and summarize representative skill packages, reusable patterns, and any obvious cautions for dependency-heavy directories. Return concise Chinese bullets. Do not modify files.","run_in_background":false,"session_id":"","subagent_type":""},"output":"SUPERVISED TASK COMPLETED SUCCESSFULLY\n\nIMPORTANT: This model (MoreCode/gemini-3-flash) is marked as unstable/experimental.\nYour run_in_background=false was automatically converted to background mode for reliability monitoring.\n\nDuration: 34s\nAgent: Sisyphus-Junior (category: quick)\n\nMONITORING INSTRUCTIONS:\n- The task was monitored and completed successfully\n- If you observe this agent behaving erratically in future calls, actively monitor its progress\n- Use background_cancel(task_id=\"...\") to abort if the agent seems stuck or producing garbage output\n- Do NOT retry automatically if you see this message - the task already succeeded\n\n---\n\nRESULT:\n\n以下是对 `capability-library/skill-library` 目录的快速检查与总结：\n\n### 代表性技能包\n*   **elite-longterm-memory-1.2.3**: 复杂的长效记忆系统，结合了 LanceDB 向量搜索、Git-Notes 知识图谱和 WAL（预写日志）协议。\n*   **openclaw-github-assistant-2.0.1**: 典型的 API 集成型技能，提供仓库管理、CI 状态检查及 Issue 创建等 GitHub 操作能力。\n*   **opencode-capability-skill**: 针对 OpenCode 运行时的操作指南，包含 Agent 设计模板、自定义工具（Plugin）注册模式及 CLI 工作流规范。\n*   **indextts / whisper-local-stt**: 专用领域的音视频/多媒体处理工具，包含本地部署的 TTS 和 STT（语音转文字）能力。\n\n### 复用模式\n*   **SKILL.md 规范**: 大多数技能包以 `SKILL.md` 作为核心合约，定义技能名称、版本、描述及所需环境变量（`metadata.requires.env`）。\n*   **Agent 模板化**: 倾向于将角色（如 coder, reviewer）定义为 Markdown 模板，并存放在 `.opencode/agent/` 或全局配置目录下。\n*   **WAL (Write-Ahead Log) 协议**: 在记忆管理中采用“先写状态再响应”的模式，以确保在 Agent 崩溃或上下文压缩时数据不丢失。\n*   **多层级存储结构**: 将上下文分为 HOT（内存/临时文件）、WARM（向量库）和 COLD（永久文档/Git）三层管理。\n\n### 依赖密集型目录注意事项\n*   **Python 虚拟环境**: 类似 `indextts` 的目录包含 `.venv` 和大量 `.py` 脚本，搜索时应显式排除这些高噪声路径，避免被海量依赖文件干扰。\n*   **Node.js 模块**: 含有 `package.json` 的技能包（如 `elite-memory`）可能包含庞大的 `node_modules`，执行全局查找时需注意性能影响。\n*   **非标准 Agent 发现**: OpenCode 仅自动识别特定路径下的 Agent 文件（如 `.opencode/agent/`），在这些目录中创建临时 Agent 时需遵循其路径规范。\n*   **环境变量敏感性**: 许多集成类技能依赖 `OPENAI_API_KEY` 或 `GITHUB_TOKEN`，在测试或迁移这些目录时需确保存储方式符合安全建议（优先环境变量）。\n\n<task_metadata>\nsession_id: ses_23d998a6dffeQeb3ElLOiHZ79p\n</task_metadata>\n\nto continue: task(session_id=\"ses_23d998a6dffeQeb3ElLOiHZ79p\", load_skills=[], run_in_background=false, prompt=\"...\")","metadata":{"truncated":false,"prompt":"In D:\\agent_workspace, quickly inspect capability-library/skill-library and summarize representative skill packages, reusable patterns, and any obvious cautions for dependency-heavy directories. Return concise Chinese bullets. Do not modify files.","agent":"Sisyphus-Junior","category":"quick","load_skills":[],"description":"Survey skill library","run_in_background":false,"sessionId":"ses_23d998a6dffeQeb3ElLOiHZ79p","command":"analyze-mode","model":{"providerID":"MoreCode","modelID":"gemini-3-flash"}},"title":"Survey skill library","time":{"start":1777082987795,"end":1777083022437}},"id":"prt_dc26674d90011Tac3QxTjCINu0","sessionID":"ses_23d9a4e4dffeFPgRJE0V5TcCHZ","messageID":"msg_dc2664276001HOosd8ENsDduzY"}}
